FBIS3-55785 "drsov008_d_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Jan 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Appoints New Representative in Tomsk Region LD1101174294 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1634 GMT 11 Jan 94 LD1101174294 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow January 11 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin appointed Tuesday Anatoliy Kobzev as his representative in Tomsk region (central Siberia), the press-service of the president reported. By another presidential decree, Yeremeiy Aipin was dismissed from his post of a president's representative in the Khanty-Mansi autonomous district as elected to the new Russian legislature. [sentence as received]
